'''Roger Guyett''' was the Visual Effects Supervisor for [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']] (also had a cameo as [[Ottegru Grey]]), [[Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens|''Star Wars'': Episode VII ''The Force Awakens'']] (also served as second unit director) and [[Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker|''Star Wars'': Episode IX ''The Rise of Skywalker'']]. He received an [[Wikipedia:Academy Awards|Oscar]] nomination for his work on ''The Force Awakens''.<ref>{{SW|url=news/star-wars-the-force-awakens-receives-5-oscar-nominations|text=''Star Wars: The Force Awakens'' Receives 5 Oscar Nominations}}</ref>

